|<span data-ttu-id="db8d7-106">Параметр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db8d7-106">Parameter</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="db8d7-107">Настраивает</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db8d7-107">Configures</span></span>|  
|---------------|----------------|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.Scope>|<span data-ttu-id="db8d7-108">Пространство имен, в котором поставщик предоставляет классы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db8d7-108">The namespace in which your provider exposes classes.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.NamespaceSecurity>|<span data-ttu-id="db8d7-109">-Безопасность (DACL) пространство имен, используемое.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db8d7-109">-   The security (DACL) on the namespace used.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.HostingModel>|<span data-ttu-id="db8d7-110">Модель размещения, который будет использоваться поставщиком.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db8d7-110">-   The hosting model that will be used by the provider.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.IdentifyLevel>|<span data-ttu-id="db8d7-111">-Режим олицетворения поставщика.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db8d7-111">-   The impersonation mode of the provider.</span></span>|  
